<h2 data-section-id="qvy7sg" data-start="121" data-end="147">Şu an yapacağımız işlem</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="149" data-end="317"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Kopyala" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-18ad762e.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>GIF’i Vercel’e yükle
→ GIF linkini kontrol et
→ Mail taslağını tarayıcıda aç
→ Gmail üzerinden kendine test maili gönder
→ Butonun oyunu açtığını kontrol et</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<h1 data-section-id="1u5qrkr" data-start="319" data-end="344">1. GIF’i GitHub’a yükle</h1>
<p data-start="346" data-end="368">Önce şu dosyayı indir:</p>
<p data-start="370" data-end="441"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="behavior-btn hover:entity-accent focus-visible:focus-ring entity-underline inline cursor-pointer appearance-none border-0 bg-transparent p-0 text-start align-baseline text-inherit" type="button">GIF’i indir</button></span></p>
<p data-start="443" data-end="516">Sonra ZIP açar gibi bir işlem yapmana gerek yok; bu doğrudan GIF dosyası.</p>
<p data-start="518" data-end="576">GitHub’daki <code data-start="530" data-end="555">technarts-birthday-game</code> repository’sine gir.</p>
<p data-start="578" data-end="594">Sağ üst tarafta:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="596" data-end="631"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Kopyala" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-18ad762e.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Add file
→ Upload files</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="633" data-end="637">seç.</p>
<p data-start="639" data-end="667">İndirdiğin şu dosyayı yükle:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="669" data-end="719"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Kopyala" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-18ad762e.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>technarts-birthday-storyboard-loop.gif</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="721" data-end="766">Dosya şu diğer dosyalarla aynı yerde durmalı:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="768" data-end="849"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Kopyala" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-18ad762e.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>index.html
style.css
script.js
technarts-birthday-storyboard-loop.gif</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="851" data-end="897">En aşağı inip <strong data-start="865" data-end="883">Commit changes</strong> butonuna bas.</p>
<h1 data-section-id="1l59ca8" data-start="899" data-end="939">2. Vercel’in GIF’i yayınlamasını bekle</h1>
<p data-start="941" data-end="994">Vercel’e girip projenin <strong data-start="965" data-end="980">Deployments</strong> bölümüne bak.</p>
<p data-start="996" data-end="1012">Yeni deployment:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1014" data-end="1031"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Kopyala" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-18ad762e.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Ready</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1033" data-end="1077">olduğunda GIF internette yayınlanmış olacak.</p>
<p data-start="1079" data-end="1110">Sonra tarayıcıya şu adresi yaz:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1112" data-end="1205"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Kopyala" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-18ad762e.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>https://technarts-birthday-game.vercel.app/technarts-birthday-storyboard-loop.gif</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1207" data-end="1247">GIF ekranda açılıyorsa bu adım tamamdır.</p>
<h2 data-section-id="1nptsc5" data-start="1249" data-end="1280">3. Mail taslağını kontrol et</h2>
<p data-start="1282" data-end="1306">Şu mail dosyasını indir:</p>
<p data-start="1308" data-end="1383"><button aria-label="technarts-birthday-mail-seda.html" class="behavior-btn hover:entity-accent focus-visible:focus-ring entity-underline inline cursor-pointer appearance-none border-0 bg-transparent p-0 text-start align-baseline text-token-text-link font-medium" type="button"><span class="relative me-0.75 inline-block h-lh w-4 align-bottom"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="absolute top-1/2 h-4 w-4 -translate-y-1/2"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-18ad762e.svg#4ccaae" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span>technarts-birthday-mail-seda.html</button></p>
<p data-start="1385" data-end="1444">Dosyaya çift tıkla. Tarayıcıda mailin ön izlemesi açılacak.</p>
<p data-start="1446" data-end="1465">Şunları kontrol et:</p>
<ul data-start="1467" data-end="1607">
<li data-section-id="1w0pnda" data-start="1467" data-end="1486">
<p data-start="1469" data-end="1486">GIF görünüyor mu?</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1x29ohn" data-start="1487" data-end="1528">
<p data-start="1489" data-end="1528">“İyi ki doğdun, Seda!” yazısı doğru mu?</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1b032zx" data-start="1529" data-end="1566">
<p data-start="1531" data-end="1566">“Oyunu Başlat” butonu görünüyor mu?</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ocbekz" data-start="1567" data-end="1607">
<p data-start="1569" data-end="1607">Butona basınca canlı oyun açılıyor mu?</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 data-section-id="1iajv03" data-start="1609" data-end="1652">4. Gmail’den kendine test maili gönderme</h2>
<p data-start="1654" data-end="1797">Burada önemli bir nokta var: HTML dosyasını Gmail’e dosya eki olarak göndermek istemiyoruz. Mailin içeriği gerçekten mail gövdesinde görünmeli.</p>
<p data-start="1799" data-end="1825">En kolay ilk test yöntemi:</p>
<ol data-start="1827" data-end="1999">
<li data-section-id="177eenk" data-start="1827" data-end="1858">
<p data-start="1830" data-end="1858">HTML dosyasını Chrome’da aç.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="i8sxxj" data-start="1859" data-end="1940">
<p data-start="1862" data-end="1899">Sayfadaki mail kartının tamamını seç:</p>
<ul data-start="1903" data-end="1940">
<li data-section-id="1xa394b" data-start="1903" data-end="1915">
<p data-start="1905" data-end="1915"><code data-start="1905" data-end="1915">Ctrl + A</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="hnzjje" data-start="1919" data-end="1940">
<p data-start="1921" data-end="1940">ardından <code data-start="1930" data-end="1940">Ctrl + C</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-section-id="101clf2" data-start="1941" data-end="1955">
<p data-start="1944" data-end="1955">Gmail’i aç.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="e66o8d" data-start="1956" data-end="1978">
<p data-start="1959" data-end="1978">Yeni ileti oluştur.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1i72l4x" data-start="1979" data-end="1999">
<p data-start="1982" data-end="1999">Alıcıya şunu yaz:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2001" data-end="2035"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Kopyala" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-18ad762e.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>sedasude.dmr@gmail.com</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<ol start="6" data-start="2037" data-end="2045">
<li data-section-id="1v2c0jc" data-start="2037" data-end="2045">
<p data-start="2040" data-end="2045">Konu:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2047" data-end="2093"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Kopyala" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-18ad762e.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>🎉 Seda, doğum günü görevin hazır!</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<ol start="7" data-start="2095" data-end="2218">
<li data-section-id="1kssi95" data-start="2095" data-end="2137">
<p data-start="2098" data-end="2137">Mail gövdesine <code data-start="2113" data-end="2123">Ctrl + V</code> ile yapıştır.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1cg59ea" data-start="2138" data-end="2199">
<p data-start="2141" data-end="2199">Göndermeden önce GIF’in ve butonun göründüğünü kontrol et.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1vo81x2" data-start="2200" data-end="2218">
<p data-start="2203" data-end="2218">Kendine gönder.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="2220" data-end="2459">Bu kopyala-yapıştır yöntemi ilk görünüm testi için kullanılabilir; ancak bazı Gmail biçimlendirmeleri veya buton stilleri değişebilir. Otomatik sistemde maili HTML olarak Resend üzerinden göndereceğimiz için tasarım daha tutarlı olacaktır.</p>
<h1 data-section-id="oqggcd" data-start="2461" data-end="2491">Mail nasıl otomatik gidecek?</h1>
<p data-start="2493" data-end="2533">Otomasyon kısmında üç yapı kullanacağız:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2535" data-end="2650"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Kopyala" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-18ad762e.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Supabase → çalışan bilgileri
Vercel Cron → her gün doğum günlerini kontrol eder
Resend → maili gönderir</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2652" data-end="2840">Vercel Cron, belirli zamanlarda bir Vercel Function çalıştırabilir; Hobby planında günde bir kez çalışma bizim doğum günü kontrolümüz için yeterlidir. <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] translate-y-0.5 animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 67px;"><a href="https://vercel.com/docs/cron-jobs?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://vercel.com/docs/cron-jobs?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl pe-2 ps-1 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 67px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 items-center gap-1"><span class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full"><img alt="" width="128" height="128" class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full" src="./Selam ve sohbet zamanı_files/favicons"></span><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">Vercel</span></span><span class="-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]">+1</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
<h2 data-section-id="1ebcyb3" data-start="2842" data-end="2858">Otomatik akış</h2>
<p data-start="2860" data-end="2887">Her sabah sistem çalışacak:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2889" data-end="3083"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Kopyala" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-18ad762e.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Bugünün tarihi nedir?
↓
Supabase’de bugün doğan çalışan var mı?
↓
Varsa adını, mailini ve yaşını al
↓
Kişiye özel mail HTML’ini oluştur
↓
Resend ile gönder
↓
Gönderildi kaydı oluştur</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="3085" data-end="3212">Resend’in API’si alıcı adresi, konu ve HTML içeriği verilerek doğrudan mail gönderebilir. <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] translate-y-0.5 animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 74px;"><a href="https://resend.com/docs/api-reference/emails/send-email?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://resend.com/docs/api-reference/emails/send-email?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl pe-2 ps-1 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 74px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 items-center gap-1"><span class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full"><img alt="" width="128" height="128" class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full" src="./Selam ve sohbet zamanı_files/favicons(1)"></span><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">resend.com</span></span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
<h2 data-section-id="1qrjc3e" data-start="3214" data-end="3253">İlk otomasyon testinde ne yapacağız?</h2>
<p data-start="3255" data-end="3318">130 kişiyi hemen eklemeyeceğiz. Önce yalnızca seni ekleyeceğiz:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="3320" data-end="3400"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Kopyala" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-18ad762e.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>name: Seda
email: sedasude.dmr@gmail.com
birthday: test günü
age: 23</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="3402" data-end="3484">Daha sonra sistemi manuel olarak çalıştırıp sana otomatik test maili göndereceğiz.</p>
<p data-start="3486" data-end="3661">Bu test başarılı olunca 130 kişinin Excel/CSV listesini Supabase’e topluca aktarabiliriz; Supabase tabloya CSV içe aktarmayı destekliyor. <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] translate-y-0.5 animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 66px;"><a href="https://supabase.com/docs/guides/database/import-data?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://supabase.com/docs/guides/database/import-data?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl pe-2 ps-1 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 66px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 items-center gap-1"><span class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full"><img alt="" width="128" height="128" class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full" src="./Selam ve sohbet zamanı_files/favicons(2)"></span><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">Supabase</span></span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
<p data-start="3663" data-end="3749" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Şimdiki ilk görev: <strong data-start="3682" data-end="3749" data-is-last-node="">GIF’i GitHub’a yükle ve Vercel linkinden açıldığını kontrol et.</strong></p></div><div class="mt-1 flex w-full flex-col gap-3"><div class="w-full"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="relative h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="select-none"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-main-surface-primary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-18ad762e.svg#fa6359" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>technarts-birthday-mail-seda.html</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><div role="group" aria-label="Kod bloku görünümü" class="group/code-block-preview-toggle relative flex items-center gap-0.5"><div aria-hidden="true" class="bg-token-interactive-bg-secondary-press pointer-events-none absolute start-0 top-0 size-9 rounded-full motion-safe:transition-transform motion-safe:duration-200 motion-safe:ease-in-out translate-x-[calc(100%+2px)] group-has-[[data-code-block-preview-toggle-code]:hover]/code-block-preview-toggle:translate-x-0 group-has-[[data-code-block-preview-toggle-code]:focus-visible]/code-block-preview-toggle:translate-x-0"></div><span class="" data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria-label="Kod" aria-pressed="fals